data.description: Great opportunity for investors!!  This four bedroom 2 1/2 baths two story home has a lot of potential.  This home has wood floors and has a separate entrance that was used for a beauty shop years ago.  Other features include a carport with an attached garage as well as a 30x34 detached garage.  Home needs some work and being sold as is.
